{"tid":2421804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"721案連控方都用假歷史","createTime":"2021-02-24T18:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T10:12:54.000Z","uid":45123,"like":91,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"77f019b3fc054702c778ceb7a374b845e7eb24cb","tid":2421804,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T18:54:48.000Z","msg":"控方指白衣人先動手 黑衣人還擊<br />\n<br />\n葉官亦問及，控方開案陳詞中提到，<span class=\"red\">案發時白衣人和黑衣人在元朗站發生暴力衝突</span>，當中「暴力衝突」的意思，在葉官追問下，控方解釋當時是白衣人先動手，並以藤條和木棍襲擊黑衣人，而<span class=\"red\">黑衣人則用滅火筒及消防喉還擊</span>。<br />\n<br />\n控方又指，當黑衣人出閘及走上月台時，均有遭白衣人追打，而葉官隨即要求控方補充案情細節。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n癡撚線 直播見到根本就冇所謂黑衣人，只有普通嘅平民。無時無刻都要更改歷史，連告人都要！<br />\n為咗安然記錄係法庭審判紀錄入面做歷史紀錄再變真實。<br />\n愈審愈偏離現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870c57a61ff8cfe7161a180f495076c068d72448","tid":2421804,"uid":28195,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T19:33:12.000Z","msg":"控方咪係律政師囉，辯方係班元朗鄉黑"},{"pid":"9ecc6f61cb207e917f41ee79417071373a8dfb11","tid":2421804,"uid":45123,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"870c57a61ff8cfe7161a180f495076c068d72448","tid":2421804,"uid":28195,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T19:33:12.000Z","msg":"控方咪係律政師囉，辯方係班元朗鄉黑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T19:36:39.000Z","msg":"自己告自己 唉"},{"pid":"9be38fa14eef899782c178629e4434f22ee568d9","tid":2421804,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T20:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed9232e636d66741f88a0297e90d22bb0b67350","tid":2421804,"uid":36901,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T20:17:30.000Z","msg":"藍衣人見到白衣人調頭走<br />\n綠衣人同白衣人搭膊頭"},{"pid":"273c2000a83cdb87667d146da8bf20a628f6afd5","tid":2421804,"uid":260121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T20:38:53.000Z","msg":